# Disable line ending conversion so packwiz hashes stay consistent.
# Per https://packwiz.infra.link/tutorials/installing/packwiz-installer/
* -text

# Auto-resolve PATCHNOTES merges instead of conflicting. It's an append-at-top
# changelog: a version branch (v0.6.0, a staged patch) adds its own section while
# each release adds another on main, so a fold collides at the top every time.
# `union` keeps BOTH sides' added lines (no conflict markers), so sync-index's fold
# succeeds and never bails to a human. (A human tidies the seam / "diff vs" baseline
# when finalizing the release notes — the union is structurally correct, just not
# perfectly spaced.)
docs/PATCHNOTES.md merge=union
